case, <link linkend="NULL:CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link> is returned.</para>
<para>

</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>cursor</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="GdkCursor"><type>GdkCursor</type></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term><listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="GdkPixbuf"><type>GdkPixbuf</type></link> representing <parameter>cursor</parameter>, or <link linkend="NULL:CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link>

</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist><para role="since">Since  2.8
</para></refsect2>
